{"id": 2902, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些事现在已经变得「不说就约等于没做」？", "description": "试问哪位健身爱好者，连续30天坚持健身却能忍住不上社交网络打卡吗？", "record_count": 2149, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190415172727IyAkOiuhgXV7JcSx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 340480, "content": "不说等于不做 不炫等于不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643136}, {"id": 340484, "content": "现在听歌不看评论等于没听", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643163}, {"id": 340741, "content": "古兰经", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643894}, {"id": 340487, "content": "我丢  这个  我最有发言权了  在公司不说我在干活儿就觉得我没在干活？？？？？？服了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378753}, {"id": 340253, "content": "两个人都不说满足就约等于没做", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411759}, {"id": 340255, "content": "去旅游不发朋友圈等于没去\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 451, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1562933}, {"id": 340256, "content": "亲手烘焙，做饭 / 出去搓一顿 不拍照发朋友圈就好像没做过 / 吃过", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635421}, {"id": 340258, "content": "想问吃素的人，当你吃菜的时候，你觉得菜菜会痛吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641683}, {"id": 340259, "content": "化了妆不拍照就等于没化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641683}, {"id": 340260, "content": "不秀恩爱就等于没谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604467}, {"id": 340264, "content": "手机不能先吃，就等于没吃？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120729}, {"id": 340265, "content": "背单词不打卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342411}, {"id": 340267, "content": "读完一本书、看完一部电影不在豆瓣上打个卡、诌几句感想，就约等于没读、没看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866507}, {"id": 340268, "content": "加班不发朋友圈就等于没加（围笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720773}, {"id": 340269, "content": "上课点名不答到", "image": null, "praise_count": 381, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950214}, {"id": 340271, "content": "不发电影票照片应该进不去影厅的门", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428323}, {"id": 340272, "content": "氪金出货不晒就等于白氪（doge", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557514}, {"id": 340273, "content": "工作，兢兢业业的干 ，不说等于没做。起码会对你所做的缩水40%。 而有人做完就“说” 工作量瞬间提升40%。 这太可怕了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 302, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 340274, "content": "看过的电影没晒过电影票感觉没看过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641719}, {"id": 340275, "content": "不加班就等于没上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641683}, {"id": 340276, "content": "不算一下跑了几圈就不算跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477025}, {"id": 341044, "content": "吃饭不发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644610}, {"id": 340279, "content": "一件都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941433}, {"id": 340281, "content": "能坚持健身,却不能坚持不发和教练的自拍合影", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588258}, {"id": 340283, "content": "吃素\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 340284, "content": "出门溜达不发朋友圈等于没出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641737}, {"id": 340287, "content": "加班打卡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 340289, "content": "健身不拍照等于没健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641761}, {"id": 340290, "content": "不发登机牌就不让上飞机", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627044}, {"id": 340291, "content": "聚餐没拍照验毒，等于没聚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484562}, {"id": 340292, "content": "离婚。每次提出来都石沉海底。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537109}, {"id": 340293, "content": "学习好累", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641493}, {"id": 340294, "content": "给领导打的下手活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645829}, {"id": 340296, "content": "得，懂了，只要别人不知道都相当于没做过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519451}, {"id": 340297, "content": "说12点之前一定要睡觉=放屁\r\n（我应该没跑题吧 ...好像是跑了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 341067, "content": "干了活要会说道，不然没人知道你干的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904410}, {"id": 340300, "content": "默默享受单身生活，却被认为孤苦伶丁很不幸", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633518}, {"id": 340301, "content": "没有分手的痛，就不证明真爱过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640690}, {"id": 340302, "content": "吃火锅，锅底不是辣的就等于没吃火锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641610}, {"id": 340303, "content": "感觉不适的事大约都是如此，例如学习、健身、内向的人要投入交际活动中去、躁动的心要安安静静看完一本需要思考的非小说类书籍…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498298}, {"id": 340313, "content": "豆瓣不标记等于没听没看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580555}, {"id": 340316, "content": "跑完步，不晒出来，等于没跑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628209}, {"id": 340319, "content": "我还真没打过一次卡，想不来实际意义，不觉对自己有多大的好处，健身了2年了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640910}, {"id": 340322, "content": "受伤、打针、去医院不发朋友圈等于健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625294}, {"id": 340323, "content": "戒烟 不告诉身边的所有人就绝对会有下一支烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556043}, {"id": 340325, "content": "健身不跑步🏃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641908}, {"id": 340328, "content": "加班没有工资等于白干", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1592953}, {"id": 340332, "content": "有对象后没在朋友圈官宣就等于没对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 340333, "content": "活着不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331630}, {"id": 340334, "content": "工作啊，不说绝对等于没做，最好还能厚起脸皮吹一番，在领导眼里才算对得起自己的薪水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604076}]}